data.description: Home and 4.5 acres in country setting away from the hustle and bustle of the city. One hour drive to beautiful beaches of South Walton and Panama City Beach. Home has newer metal roof, installed September 2022. Half of the land has been cleared. Wooded area has a creek that runs along the boundary, according to the seller. Two car carport with concrete slab. Metal barn on the other side for storage. There is also a second 2-car carport. Fenced in area for pets in the front yard. Hardwood floors throughout, large living room with fire burning fireplace and cathedral ceilings, master bath with garden tub, shower, and double vanity, lots of closet space. Fronts paved road. No HOA and no restrictions.
